hrist (Caravaggio)\">The Taking of Christ</a></i> (1602)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Entombment_of_Christ_(Caravaggio)\" title=\"The Entombment of Christ (Caravaggio)\">The Entombment of Christ</a></i> (c. 1603)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Madonna_di_Loreto_(Caravaggio)\" title=\"Madonna di Loreto (Caravaggio)\">Madonna of Loreto (Madonna dei Pellegrini, Pilgrims' Madonna)</a></i> (c. 1604)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Crowning_with_Thorns_(Prato)\" title=\"The Crowning with Thorns (Prato)\">The Crowning with Thorns (Prato)</a></i> (1604)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Death_of_the_Virgin_(Caravaggio)\" title=\"Death of the Virgin (Caravaggio)\">The Death of the Virgin</a></i> (1604)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Saint_Francis_in_Meditation_(Caravaggio)\" title=\"Saint Francis in Meditation (Caravaggio)\">Saint Francis in Meditation</a></i> (c. 1603)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Christ_on_the_Mount_of_Olives_(Caravaggio)\" title=\"Christ on the Mount of Olives (Caravaggio)\">Christ on the Mount of Olives</a></i> (1605)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Ecce_Homo_(Caravaggio)\" title=\"Ecce Homo (Caravaggio)\">Ecce Homo</a></i> (c. 1605)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Saint_Jerome_in_Meditation_(Caravaggio)\" title=\"Saint Jerome in Meditation (Caravaggio)\">Saint Jerome in Meditation</a></i> (c. 1605)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Saint_Jerome_Writing\" title=\"Saint Jerome Writing\"><i>Saint Jerome Writing</i> (Borghese)</a> (c. 1605)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Portrait_of_Pope_Paul_V\" title=\"Portrait of Pope Paul V\">Portrait of Pope Paul V</a></i> (1605)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Still_Life_with_Fruit_(Caravaggio)\" title=\"Still Life with Fruit (Caravaggio)\">Still Life with Fruit</a></i> (1605)</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Madonna_and_Child_with_St._Anne_(Dei_Palafrenieri)\" title=\"Madonna and Child with St. Anne (Dei Palafrenieri)\">Madonna and Child with St. Anne (Madonna de Palafrenieri)</a></i> (1606)</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" cla